  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Question-- Witness, you have told a tribunal that in July 1942, some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 75 Polish girls, who were in the transport from Lublin, were called before the camp doctors in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, were any of these girls selected for an operation?'",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, this young woman testified in Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, it had to be interpreted into German and English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 'On this day, we did not know why we were called before the camp doctors.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the same day, 10 of 25 girls were taken to the hospital, but we did not know why.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were called at a time when executions usually took place, and I thought I was going to be executed because some girls had been shot down before.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the hospital, we were put to bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the ward in which we stayed was locked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then a German nurse arrived and gave me an injection in my leg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After this injection, I vomited and I was weak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I lost consciousness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I regained consciousness in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I noticed that my leg was in a cast, from my ankle up to the knee.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I felt very great pain in this leg and had a high temperature.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I noticed also that my leg was swollen, from the toes up to the groin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I felt great pain, and I had the impression that something must have been cut out of my leg.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Two weeks later, the bandage was removed, and that was the first time I saw my leg.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The incision was so deep that I could see the bone.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
